---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 379
  - Title: Rosarium Philosophorum
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Return to the Womb of
    the Mother
---
Beya mounted upon Gabricus and enclosed him in her womb in such manner
that nothing more was visible of him. She embraced him with so much
love that she absorbed him completely into her own nature.
